// PobTools application icon (icon/pobtools_icon_version_b).
//
// One resource serves every surface:
//  - Explorer / taskbar use the exe's first RT_GROUP_ICON;
//  - GLFW window classes (launcher / editors / atlas planner) load the icon
//    resource named exactly "GLFW_ICON";
//  - the PoB engine window (sys_programIcons_c in sys_video.cpp) enumerates the
//    running exe's first icon group at runtime.
GLFW_ICON ICON "pobtools.ico"
